

ASKCC                 Environmental Variable                ASKCC




Force prompting for CC names

AASSKKCCCC=_Y_E_S/_N_O

The  environmental variable  ASKCC  directs the  program mail  to
prompt for  carbon-copy names.  A carbon-copy  (or CC) name gives
another person to whom a mail message should be sent.  To turn on
prompting, use the command:


        export ASKCC=YES


***** See Also *****

